'''Tinml''' nɣ '''Aɣrbaz''' (s taclḥit takuyast: '''Sskwila''' nɣ '''Lmdṛṣt''') iga tasntut n usslmd nna ɣ ttlmadn inlmadn timsirin d kigan n tussniwin, da gis tettili tɣri s tugt n tmsirin igan tamnzut d tanammast d tasmuttgt tasinant, ism nns tiɣri tamnzut n bzziz ɣ kigan n tmizar. Da bṭṭun tinmal s tinmal n tnbaḍt d tinmal tusligin d tinmal tignsanin.

Ɣ tugt n tmizar, ur igi wadduy s tinml s bzziz, maca iga "usslmd n iḥnjirn" mkann. lla kra tdrsa g ibabatn nna istin ad sslmdn tarwa nnsn ɣ tgmmi . Issnti usslmd n bzziz zɣ usggas wis sḍiṣ nɣ wis sa ɣ wawtay n warraw.

Issnti usslmd n bzziz s wadaf s tinml ɣ usggas wis sḍis. Ɣ tmsirt ad ittktasab uḥnjir tirsal n tiɣri d tirra d usiḍn. Tga tmsirt bahra imqqurn acku da tettaws i unlmad d ar tbnnu tamadant nns. tmqqur bahra mk ttawsn iɣrbaɣn ɣ usbuɣlj n tiwangimin n inlmadn d twisi f urmas (afhm).

